# 2026-04-08 (wizardly merge): allow the rebuild-time archive subtree so old
# tracked artifacts (e.g. ONNX exports) can be `git mv`d into archive/. Use
# `artifacts/*` instead of `artifacts/` so the negation can re-include the
# archive subdirectory (gitignore won't recurse into a fully-ignored dir).
artifacts/*
!artifacts/archive/

